Title: Door Zone Hazard Sign
Date: 2011-12-14
Topics: cycling design idea

Here’s another idea of a hazard sign for cycle lanes, continuing form [my previous post][0]. Cyclists sometimes travel too near the left edge of the road, or too close to parked cars for safety. Cycle lanes should not encourage this.

